{"tid":212570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小偽虎鯨銅鑼灣避風塘慘死 屍身嚴重腐爛","createTime":"2017-04-22T14:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T10:51:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"613e2e43988599af21d891d950b403645dd46dd4","tid":212570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170422/large/1492853542_63d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170422%2Flarge%2F1492853542_63d6.jpg&h=39e8a58d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港海洋公園保育基金今早9時接報，一條偽虎鯨擱淺於銅鑼灣避風塘。保育基金人員到場後，證實擱淺的偽虎鯨已死亡，屍身嚴重腐爛，屬第四級，初步估計，死去的偽虎鯨為雄性，年幼，惟因鯨屍體積較大，身長3.60米，難以運輸，鯨豚擱淺行動組將把其頭顱、胸鰭及內臟運返海洋公園，作進一步檢驗，以便了解死因，暫未能確定死因。<br />\n<br />\n偽虎鯨是全球體型第四大的海豚，屬於外海品種。牠主要出沒於亞熱帶及溫帶的開放水域，成年雄性體長可達6米。本港分別於1983、2000、2002及2005年發生偽虎鯨擱淺個案；而在香港水域發現偽虎鯨出沒的記錄分別為1996及2014年。<br />\n香港海洋公園保育基金呼籲公眾，若發現懷疑鯨豚擱淺個案，可致電1823熱線，並提供發現擱淺的時間、地點、相片(如有)，讓行動組能盡快到場跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170422/56599410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170422%2F56599410&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=3d7fb78f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170422%2F56599410&h=51912327\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170422/56599410</a>"},{"pid":"3f36533e7d92997b0ae3936f8c7c5c8112b19ddc","tid":212570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6a44bc86c527e8b7d6502b74c104080a4e4a3c","tid":212570,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4120880b998361